msgid "Good to know:"
msgstr "Bra att veta:"

#: install/index.php:434
msgid ""
"Use your callsign as your username for QRZ.com. The XML API does not support "
"email addresses."
msgstr ""
"Använd din anropssignal som ditt användarnamn för QRZ.com. XML API stöder "
"inte e-postadresser."

